description: emerald hills under a golden sunrise',
code:
<svg viewBox="0 0 200 100" width="200" height="100" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <!-- Background for the sky -->
  <rect x="0" y="0" width="200" height="100" fill="lightblue" />
  
  <!-- Sun -->
  <circle cx="160" cy="20" r="15" fill="gold" />
  
  <!-- Hills -->
  <path d="M0 60 Q50 30 100 60 T200 60 L200 100 L0 100 Z" fill="green" />
  
  <!-- Gradient for the sunrise effect -->
  <defs>
    <linearGradient id="sunriseGradient" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
      <stop offset="0%" stop-color="gold" stop-opacity="0.8" />
      <stop offset="100%" stop-color="lightblue" stop-opacity="0" />
    </linearGradient>
  </defs>
  
  <!-- Overlay gradient for sunrise effect -->
  <rect x="0" y="0" width="200" height="100" fill="url(#sunriseGradient)" />
</svg>

<svg viewBox="0 0 200 100" width="400" height="200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <!-- Background: Sky and Sea -->
  <rect x="0" y="0" width="200" height="50" fill="#87CEEB" /> <!-- Sky -->
  <rect x="0" y="50" width="200" height="50" fill="#1E90FF" /> <!-- Sea -->

  <!-- Sun -->
  <circle cx="180" cy="20" r="10" fill="#FFD700" />

  <!-- Coastal Town: Houses -->
  <rect x="20" y="40" width="10" height="10" fill="#8B4513" /> <!-- House 1 -->
  <rect x="35" y="35" width="10" height="15" fill="#A0522D" /> <!-- House 2 -->
  <rect x="50" y="40" width="10" height="10" fill="#8B4513" /> <!-- House 3 -->

  <!-- Fishing Boats -->
  <g transform="translate(80, 55)">
    <!-- Boat 1 -->
    <polygon points="0,0 20,0 15,5 5,5" fill="#FF6347" /> <!-- Hull -->
    <line x1="10" y1="0" x2="10" y2="-10" stroke="#000000" stroke-width="1" /> <!-- Mast -->
    <polygon points="10,-10 5,-5 15,-5" fill="#FFFFFF" /> <!-- Sail -->
  </g>
  <g transform="translate(120, 50)">
    <!-- Boat 2 -->
    <polygon points="0,0 20,0 15,5 5,5" fill="#FFA500" /> <!-- Hull -->
    <line x1="10" y1="0" x2="10" y2="-10" stroke="#000000" stroke-width="1" /> <!-- Mast -->
    <polygon points="10,-10 5,-5 15,-5" fill="#FFFFFF" /> <!-- Sail -->
  </g>
  <g transform="translate(160, 55)">
    <!-- Boat 3 -->
    <polygon points="0,0 20,0 15,5 5,5" fill="#32CD32" /> <!-- Hull -->
    <line x1="10" y1="0" x2="10" y2="-10" stroke="#000000" stroke-width="1" /> <!-- Mast -->
    <polygon points="10,-10 5,-5 15,-5" fill="#FFFFFF" /> <!-- Sail -->
  </g>

  <!-- Waves -->
  <path d="M0,60 Q10,55 20,60 T40,60 T60,60 T80,60 T100,60 T120,60 T140,60 T160,60 T180,60 T200,60" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" />
</svg>

<svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" width="200" height="200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">

  <defs>
    <linearGradient id="plateGradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="0%" y2="100%">
      <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#f0f0f0" />
      <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#d0d0d0" />
    </linearGradient>
    <linearGradient id="mustardGradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="0%" y2="100%">
      <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#e6d800" />
      <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#d4c200" />
    </linearGradient>
  </defs>
  
  <!-- Plate -->
  <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="80" fill="url(#plateGradient)" stroke="#b0b0b0" stroke-width="2"/>
  <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="70" fill="#f8f8f8" stroke="#c0c0c0" stroke-width="1"/>
  
  <!-- Grilled Mustard Tops -->
  <g transform="translate(60, 60)">
    <!-- First mustard top -->
    <ellipse cx="20" cy="20" rx="25" ry="8" fill="url(#mustardGradient)" opacity="0.9" transform="rotate(-15 20 20)"/>
    <polygon points="15,20 25,20 30,40 10,40" fill="#b39b00" opacity="0.7"/>
    
    <!-- Second mustard top -->
    <ellipse cx="60" cy="30" rx="20" ry="6" fill="url(#mustardGradient)" opacity="0.9" transform="rotate(10 60 30)"/>
    <polygon points="55,30 65,30 68,45 52,45" fill="#b39b00" opacity="0.7"/>
    
    <!-- Third mustard top -->
    <ellipse cx="40" cy="50" rx="18" ry="5" fill="url(#mustardGradient)" opacity="0.9" transform="rotate(-5 40 50)"/>
    <polygon points="37,50 43,50 45,60 35,60" fill="#b39b00" opacity="0.7"/>
    
    <!-- Grill marks -->
    <line x1="15" y1="25" x2="25" y2="25" stroke="#8b6b00" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="55" y1="35" x2="65" y2="35" stroke="#8b6b00" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="35" y1="55" x2="45" y2="55" stroke="#8b6b00" stroke-width="1"/>
  </g>
</svg>

description: A dense jungle with a wooden bridge
code:
<svg viewBox="0 0 400 300" width="400" height="300" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <defs>
    <linearGradient id="sky" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
      <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#87CEEB" />
      <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#E0F7FA" />
    </linearGradient>
  </defs>
  
  <!-- Background -->
  <rect width="400" height="300" fill="url(#sky)" />
  
  <!-- Jungle canopy -->
  <g fill="#2E8B57" opacity="0.8">
    <ellipse cx="50" cy="50" rx="60" ry="40" />
    <ellipse cx="120" cy="40" rx="70" ry="50" />
    <ellipse cx="200" cy="30" rx="80" ry="60" />
    <ellipse cx="280" cy="50" rx="90" ry="50" />
    <ellipse cx="350" cy="40" rx="70" ry="40" />
    <ellipse cx="50" cy="100" rx="50" ry="30" />
    <ellipse cx="380" cy="90" rx="60" ry="35" />
  </g>
  
  <!-- Tree trunks -->
  <g fill="#5D4037">
    <rect x="50" y="120" width="15" height="180" />
    <rect x="120" y="110" width="12" height="190" />
    <rect x="200" y="100" width="18" height="200" />
    <rect x="280" y="110" width="14" height="190" />
    <rect x="350" y="120" width="16" height="180" />
  </g>
  
  <!-- Wooden bridge -->
  <g fill="#8B4513">
    <!-- Bridge planks -->
    <rect x="100" y="200" width="200" height="10" />
    <rect x="100" y="180" width="200" height="5" />
    <rect x="100" y="160" width="200" height="5" />
    
    <!-- Bridge sides -->
    <rect x="100" y="160" width="10" height="50" />
    <rect x="290" y="160" width="10" height="50" />
    
    <!-- Bridge ropes -->
    <line x1="100" y1="160" x2="50" y2="140" stroke="#5D4037" stroke-width="3" />
    <line x1="300" y1="160" x2="350" y2="140" stroke="#5D4037" stroke-width="3" />
  </g>
  
  <!-- Ground -->
  <rect x="0" y="250" width="400" height="50" fill="#4CAF50" />
  
  <!-- Additional jungle plants -->
  <g fill="#388E3C">
    <ellipse cx="30" cy="230" rx="25" ry="15" />
    <ellipse cx="370" cy="240" rx="30" ry="20" />
    <ellipse cx="150" cy="230" rx="20" ry="12" />
    <ellipse cx="250" cy="235" rx="25" ry="15" />
  </g>
</svg>

description: Glass of sparkling water with lime
code:
<svg viewBox="0 0 100 150" width="200" height="300" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <defs>
    <linearGradient id="glassGradient" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
      <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#d1e8f2" stop-opacity="0.8"/>
      <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#a8d5e5" stop-opacity="0.3"/>
    </linearGradient>
    <linearGradient id="bubbleGradient" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
      <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#ffffff" stop-opacity="0.9"/>
      <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#e6f7ff" stop-opacity="0.5"/>
    </linearGradient>
  </defs>
  
  <!-- Glass outline -->
  <path d="M30,20 L30,120 Q50,130 70,120 L70,20 Q50,10 30,20 Z" 
        fill="url(#glassGradient)" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1"/>
  
  <!-- Water surface -->
  <ellipse cx="50" cy="30" rx="18" ry="5" fill="#e6f7ff" opacity="0.7"/>
  
  <!-- Bubbles -->
  <circle cx="40" cy="50" r="2" fill="url(#bubbleGradient)"/>
  <circle cx="55" cy="45" r="1.5" fill="url(#bubbleGradient)"/>
  <circle cx="45" cy="70" r="2.5" fill="url(#bubbleGradient)"/>
  <circle cx="60" cy="65" r="1.8" fill="url(#bubbleGradient)"/>
  <circle cx="50" cy="90" r="2" fill="url(#bubbleGradient)"/>
  <circle cx="35" cy="85" r="1.5" fill="url(#bubbleGradient)"/>
  
  <!-- Lime slice -->
  <g transform="translate(45,60) rotate(15)">
    <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="12" fill="#8bc34a" opacity="0.8"/>
    <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="10" fill="#aed581"/>
    <path d="M0,-10 L5,-5 L10,-10 L5,-15 Z" fill="#f1f8e9"/>
    <line x1="-5" y1="5" x2="5" y2="-5" stroke="#5d8c2a" stroke-width="1"/>
  </g>
  
  <!-- Glass base -->
  <ellipse cx="50" cy="120" rx="20" ry="5" fill="#f5f5f5" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1"/>
</svg>

description: Bubbles floating upward in transparent layers
code:
<svg viewBox="0 0 200 300" width="400" height="600" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <defs>
    <radialGradient id="bubbleGradient" cx="0.3" cy="0.3" r="0.7">
      <stop offset="0%" stop-color="white" stop-opacity="0.8"/>
      <stop offset="100%" stop-color="lightblue" stop-opacity="0.3"/>
    </radialGradient>
  </defs>
  
  <!-- Background layers with transparency -->
  <rect x="0" y="0" width="200" height="300" fill="lightblue" opacity="0.1"/>
  
  <!-- Bubble layer 1 (bottom) -->
  <g opacity="0.7">
    <circle cx="50" cy="250" r="15" fill="url(#bubbleGradient)" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.5"/>
    <circle cx="120" cy="220" r="10" fill="url(#bubbleGradient)" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.5"/>
    <circle cx="80" cy="280" r="8" fill="url(#bubbleGradient)" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.5"/>
  </g>
  
  <!-- Bubble layer 2 (middle) -->
  <g opacity="0.8">
    <circle cx="30" cy="180" r="12" fill="url(#bubbleGradient)" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.5"/>
    <circle cx="150" cy="150" r="18" fill="url(#bubbleGradient)" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.5"/>
    <circle cx="90" cy="130" r="7" fill="url(#bubbleGradient)" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.5"/>
  </g>
  
  <!-- Bubble layer 3 (top) -->
  <g opacity="0.9">
    <circle cx="70" cy="70" r="14" fill="url(#bubbleGradient)" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.5"/>
    <circle cx="140" cy="40" r="9" fill="url(#bubbleGradient)" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.5"/>
    <circle cx="180" cy="80" r="6" fill="url(#bubbleGradient)" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.5"/>
  </g>
  
  <!-- Rising bubble paths -->
  <g opacity="0.4">
    <polyline points="50,250 45,200 50,150" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.3"/>
    <polyline points="120,220 125,170 120,120" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.3"/>
    <polyline points="150,150 155,100 150,50" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.3"/>
  </g>
</svg>

description: Futuristic neon grid lines glowing in the dark
code:
<svg viewBox="0 0 400 400" width="400" height="400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <defs>
    <linearGradient id="neonGlow" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
      <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#00f0ff" stop-opacity="0.8"/>
      <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#ff00f0" stop-opacity="0.8"/>
    </linearGradient>
    <filter id="glow" x="-30%" y="-30%" width="160%" height="160%">
      <feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="4" result="blur"/>
      <feComposite in="SourceGraphic" in2="blur" operator="over"/>
    </filter>
  </defs>
  
  <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="#0a0a1a"/>
  
  <g stroke="url(#neonGlow)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-opacity="0.9" filter="url(#glow)">
    <!-- Vertical grid lines -->
    <line x1="50" y1="0" x2="50" y2="400"/>

    <line x1="150" y1="0" x2="150" y2="400"/>

    <line x1="300" y1="0" x2="300" y2="400"/>

<svg viewBox="0 0 200 100" width="400" height="200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">

      <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#00f0ff" stop-opacity="0.8"/>
      <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#ff00f0" stop-opacity="0.8"/>

          stroke-width="3"/>

          fill="none" 
          stroke="url(#neonGlow)" 
          stroke-width="3"/>
    
    <!-- Bottom arc -->
    <path d="M20 50 Q100 70 180 50" 
          fill="none" 
          stroke="url(#neonGlow)" 
          stroke-width="3"/>
  </g>
</svg>

    <radialGradient id="glow" cx="0.5" cy="0.5" r="0.5">
      <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#00f7ff" stop-opacity="0.8"/>
      <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#0066ff" stop-opacity="0"/>
    </radialGradient>
    <linearGradient id="smoke" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
      <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#ffffff"/>
      <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#00f7ff"/>
    </linearGradient>
  </defs>
  
  <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="#000033"/>
  
  <!-- Glowing background effect -->
  <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="80" fill="url(#glow)" opacity="0.7"/>
  
  <!-- Swirling smoke paths -->
  <g fill="none" stroke="url(#smoke)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
    <path d="M40,80 C60,40 80,60 100,40 C120,60 140,40 160,80" opacity="0.8"/>
    <path d="M50,100 C70,70 90,90 110,70 C130,90 150,70 170,100" opacity="0.7"/>
    <path d="M60,120 C80,100 100,120 120,100 C140,120 160,100 180,120" opacity="0.6"/>
    <path d="M30,140 C50,110 70,130 90,110 C110,130 130,110 150,140" opacity="0.5"/>
  </g>
  
  <!-- Additional glowing elements -->
  <circle cx="70" cy="70" r="3" fill="#00f7ff" opacity="0.9"/>
  <circle cx="130" cy="90" r="2" fill="#00f7ff" opacity="0.8"/>
  <circle cx="90" cy="130" r="2" fill="#00f7ff" opacity="0.7"/>
</svg>

description: Sunlight through autumn leaves
code:
<svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" width="400" height="400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <defs>
    <radialGradient id="sunlight" cx="0.5" cy="0.5" r="0.5">
      <stop offset="0%" stop-color="yellow" stop-opacity="0.8"/>
      <stop offset="100%" stop-color="orange" stop-opacity="0.1"/>
    </radialGradient>
  </defs>
  
  <!-- Background sky -->
  <rect x="0" y="0" width="200" height="200" fill="lightblue"/>
  
  <!-- Sun rays -->
  <g fill="url(#sunlight)" opacity="0.7">
    <polygon points="100,0 110,20 130,10 120,30 140,30 120,50 130,70 110,60 100,80 90,60 70,70 80,50 60,30 80,30 70,10 90,20"/>
  </g>
  
  <!-- Autumn leaves -->
  <g transform="translate(0,30)">
    <!-- Leaf 1 -->
    <g transform="translate(50,40) rotate(-20)">
      <path d="M0,0 C10,-15 25,-20 40,-10 C35,5 15,15 0,0 Z" fill="orange"/>
      <line x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="15" stroke="brown" stroke-width="1.5"/>
    </g>
    
    <!-- Leaf 2 -->
    <g transform="translate(120,30) rotate(10)">
      <path d="M0,0 C15,-10 30,-5 30,10 C15,20 0,15 0,0 Z" fill="red"/>
      <line x1="15" y1="10" x2="15" y2="25" stroke="brown" stroke-width="1.5"/>
    </g>
    
    <!-- Leaf 3 -->
    <g transform="translate(80,80) rotate(45)">
      <path d="M0,0 C10,-20 30,-15 25,5 C10,20 -5,10 0,0 Z" fill="gold"/>
      <line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="20" stroke="brown" stroke-width="1.5"/>
    </g>
    
    <!-- Falling leaves -->
    <g opacity="0.8">
      <path d="M160,10 C165,15 170,12 170,5 C165,0 160,3 160,10 Z" fill="orangered" transform="rotate(-15,165,7)"/>
      <path d="M180,50 C185,55 190,52 190,45 C185,40 180,43 180,50 Z" fill="gold" transform="rotate(10,185,47)"/>
      <path d="M140,90 C145,95 150,92 150,85 C145,80 140,83 140,90 Z" fill="orange" transform="rotate(-5,145,87)"/>
    </g>
  </g>
  
  <!-- Light beams -->
  <g stroke="yellow" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.4">
    <line x1="100" y1="0" x2="60" y2="50"/>
    <line x1="100" y1="0" x2="90" y2="70"/>
    <line x1="100" y1="0" x2="130" y2="60"/>
    <line x1="100" y1="0" x2="150" y2="40"/>
  </g>
</svg>

<svg viewBox="0 0 400 300" width="400" height="300" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <defs>
    <radialGradient id="sun" cx="0.5" cy="0.5" r="0.5">
      <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#FFD700" />
      <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#FF8C00" />
    </radialGradient>
    <radialGradient id="petal" cx="0.5" cy="0.5" r="0.5">
      <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#FFD700" />
      <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#F4A460" />
    </radialGradient>
  </defs>

  <!-- Background - luminous field -->
  <rect x="0" y="0" width="400" height="300" fill="#87CEEB" opacity="0.8" />
  <rect x="0" y="200" width="400" height="100" fill="#7CFC00" />
  
  <!-- Sun rays -->
  <g fill="#FFFFFF" opacity="0.3">
    <polygon points="200,50 210,70 230,70 215,85 225,105 200,95 175,105 185,85 170,70 190,70" />
    <polygon points="50,150 70,140 70,160" transform="rotate(45, 50, 150)" />
    <polygon points="350,150 330,140 330,160" transform="rotate(-45, 350, 150)" />
  </g>

  <!-- Sunflower stem -->
  <line x1="200" y1="200" x2="200" y2="120" stroke="#228B22" stroke-width="8" />
  
  <!-- Sunflower leaves -->
  <g fill="#32CD32">
    <ellipse cx="170" cy="160" rx="25" ry="15" transform="rotate(-30, 170, 160)" />
    <ellipse cx="230" cy="160" rx="25" ry="15" transform="rotate(30, 230, 160)" />
  </g>

  <!-- Sunflower center -->
  <circle cx="200" cy="120" r="25" fill="url(#sun)" />
  
  <!-- Sunflower petals -->
  <g fill="url(#petal)" stroke="#DAA520" stroke-width="0.5">
    <ellipse cx="150" cy="120" rx="20" ry="10" transform="rotate(0, 150, 120)" />
    <ellipse cx="170" cy="100" rx="20" ry="10" transform="rotate(30, 170, 100)" />
    <ellipse cx="200" cy="90" rx="20" ry="10" transform="rotate(60, 200, 90)" />
    <ellipse cx="230" cy="100" rx="20" ry="10" transform="rotate(90, 230, 100)" />
    <ellipse cx="250" cy="120" rx="20" ry="10" transform="rotate(120, 250, 120)" />
    <ellipse cx="230" cy="140" rx="20" ry="10" transform="rotate(150, 230, 140)" />
    <ellipse cx="200" cy="150" rx="20" ry="10" transform="rotate(180, 200, 150)" />
    <ellipse cx="170" cy="140" rx="20" ry="10" transform="rotate(210, 170, 140)" />
  </g>

  <!-- Sunflower seeds -->
  <g fill="#8B4513">
    <circle cx="195" cy="115" r="2" />
    <circle cx="205" cy="115" r="2" />
    <circle cx="200" cy="120" r="2" />
    <circle cx="195" cy="125" r="2" />
    <circle cx="205" cy="125" r="2" />
  </g>
</svg>

description: Abstract shapes resembling floating paper

<svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" width="400" height="400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <defs>
    <linearGradient id="paperGradient1" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
      <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#f5f5f5" />
      <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#e0e0e0" />
    </linearGradient>
    <linearGradient id="paperGradient2" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
      <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#e8f4f8" />
      <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#d0e9f1" />
    </linearGradient>
  </defs>
  
  <g transform="rotate(-5 100 100)">
    <!-- Main paper shape -->
    <polygon points="30,40 170,50 160,160 40,150" 
             fill="url(#paperGradient1)" 
             stroke="#cccccc" 
             stroke-width="1" />
             
    <!-- Folded corner effect -->
    <polygon points="140,50 170,50 160,80" 
             fill="#f0f0f0" 
             stroke="#cccccc" 
             stroke-width="0.5" />
  </g>
  
  <g transform="rotate(10 100 100) translate(20 -10)">
    <!-- Secondary paper shape -->
    <polygon points="80,80 150,90 130,130 60,120" 
             fill="url(#paperGradient2)" 
             stroke="#b3d9e6" 
             stroke-width="1" />
             
    <!-- Shadow effect -->
    <polygon points="60,120 130,130 125,135 55,125" 
             fill="#000000" 
             opacity="0.1" />
  </g>
  
  <!-- Small floating paper piece -->
  <g transform="rotate(-15 100 100) translate(30 20)">
    <rect x="20" y="100" width="40" height="30" 
          rx="2" ry="2" 
          fill="#ffffff" 
          stroke="#dddddd" 
          stroke-width="0.5" />
    <line x1="25" y1="105" x2="55" y2="105" 
          stroke="#eeeeee" 
          stroke-width="1" />
  </g>
</svg>
